cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for gait recognition, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of autoencoders, which are a type of neural network, indicating that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of video data, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper addresses security applications, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
